      <title>俄罗斯石油卡在印度被禁止的船上找到新油轮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/russian-oil-stuck-on-india-banned-ship-finds-new-tanker</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一艘被印度港口当局拒绝的船上的俄罗斯原油货物现在被转移到另一艘油轮，船舶跟踪数据显示，这表明交易者如何找到避免敏感运费的监管障碍的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/russian-oil-stuck-on-india-banned-ship-finds-new-tanker</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 06:28:23 GMT</pubDate>
