      <title>桑坦德确认目标，认为季度的盈利能力在</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/santander-confirms-targets-sees-profitability-rising-in-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Banco Santander SA表示，它预计第一季度的盈利能力将有一个关键的衡量标准，这首先表明西班牙最大的贷方在今年年初的表现如何。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/santander-confirms-targets-sees-profitability-rising-in-quarter</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 06:18:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
