      <title>Yardeni说，美国股票SWOON提供“绝佳的购买机会”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/yardeni-says-us-stock-swoon-offers-great-buying-opportunity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据华尔街老将爱德华·耶尔德尼（Edward Yardeni）称，由于担心经济衰退，投资者应购买美国股票的下跌。]]></description>
