    <item>
      <title>在惊喜欧佩克+远足之后，石油扩大了急剧下降，特朗普关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税和欧佩克+决定增加产出速度之后，石油进一步下降了，这比先前宣布的更快触发了自2022年以来最严重的溃败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-4</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 22:53:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰中央银行首席树桩市场，速率降低了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/polish-central-bank-chief-stumps-markets-with-pivot-to-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰中央银行家亚当·格拉平斯基（Adam Glapinski）具有全有或全无的风格，很难掌握金融市场。在坚持没有贷款宽松的一周后，州长说，他可能会在5月份提出一项动议，以降低利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/polish-central-bank-chief-stumps-markets-with-pivot-to-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 17:19:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
